item.title: Wroclaw South
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: A large parking lot with convenient access located in the southern part of the city. Open also on weekends.

item.title: Wroclaw Old Town
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Located in the very center of the old town, the car park will accommodate several dozen cars, several buses including motorhomes and caravans. Car park open around the clock.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Using a meet and greet service means you don't have to drive to the car park at all. The drivers are always professional and experienced, fully capable of taking charge of your vehicle.
The service allows travellers to quickly and smoothly pass through car park security control bypassing the queue for vans and buses.

item.title: Parking at the Museum
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: The car park is located directly at the Museum. There are 65 wide car park spaces, of which 20 are covered.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Want to return home from your trip to a gorgeous, clean car? Get your car cleaned whilst you park. The service includes exterior wash and dry by hand, tyres glossed and protective wax.
Take advantage of the shuttle service from the car park to the city center. The price depends on the number of people.
